Package: crashcounter
Type: Package
Title: Generate crash counts for road segments
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Wood", "Jonathan", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jwood2@iastate.edu", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0131-6384")))
Maintainer: Jonathan Wood <jwood2@iastate.edu>
Description: Uses `dplyr`, `sf`, and `tidyr` to combine to get crash counts for roadways and intersections. This uses spatial or linear-referencing system (LRS) data to get crash counts for roadways and intersections. 
